The Chinese Communist Party is buying up influence
around the world!

245
00:11:21,850 --> 00:11:24,200
That’s why this is an urgent call to our
fans.

246
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,950
If you like how we uncensor China,

247
00:11:26,950 --> 00:11:29,350
consider joining our 50-cent army.

248
